### 🎯 **Key Design Decisions**

✓ **Binary Columnar Format**: Zero-copy mmap access (no text parsing overhead)
✓ **DECIMAL as int64_t**: Scaled by 100 (e.g., 0.05 → 5) — eliminates IEEE 754 errors
✓ **DATE as int32_t**: Days since epoch (1970-01-01 = 0, verified by self-test)
✓ **Dictionary Encoding**: Low-cardinality strings as int32_t codes + dict files
✓ **Sort Order**: lineitem(l_shipdate), orders(o_orderkey), customer(c_custkey)
✓ **Parallelization**: 32 cores used throughout ingestion and index building

